boards%2Fch-911901a-na%2Fk70-rgb-tkl-champion-series-optical-mechanical-gaming-keyboard-with-pbt-double-shot-pro-keycaps-na-ch-911901a-na" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.corsair.com/us/en/p/keyboards/ch-911901a-na/k70-rgb-tkl-champion-series-optical-mechanical-gaming-keyboard-with-pbt-double-shot-pro-keycaps-na-ch-911901a-na">Corsair K70 RGB TKL</a>是一款不错的基本中端型号，但与 Huntsman V2 TKL 相比，它的噪音也较大，并且配备了中等软件。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-04/9aeda4a0-f5e7-11ee-b966-b6c4d36f6f10" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-04/9aeda4a0-f5e7-11ee-b966-b6c4d36f6f10" style="height:1201px;width:2000px;" alt="黑色罗技 G Pro X 60 无线游戏键盘位于木质桌面上，键帽显示浅蓝色 RGB 背光。" data-uuid="a2b41081-fc78-3c5d-a708-289bc425b2d2"><figcaption>罗技 G Pro X 60。</figcaption><div class="photo-credit">摄影：Jeff Dunn / Engadget</div></figure><h3 id="jump-link-logitech-g-pro-x-tkl-and-g-pro-x-60">罗技 G Pro X TKL 和 G Pro X 60</h3><p>无线<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAevOuoOmegABpntBt4KpcYoxFHQq29lthzmJIvMAXxzX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-Lightspeed-Ultra-Portable-Tenkeyless-LIGHTSYNC%2Fdp%2FB0BQBRPZ8M" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/Logitech-Lightspeed-Ultra-Portable-Tenkeyless-LIGHTSYNC/dp/B0BQBRPZ8M">罗技 G Pro X TKL</a>和<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAX8xJmGFHm1MqlI5uGrxUIqDpnTMvAbzsKCBnah0_FF3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FLogitech-Lightspeed-Ultra-Portable-Tenkeyless-LIGH